<h1>Job Letter Application</h1>

<div class="gf_browser_chrome gform_wrapper" id="gform_wrapper_1"><a id="gf_1" name="gf_1"
                                                                     class="gform_anchor"></a>

        <div class="gform_body">
            <ul id="gform_fields_1" class="gform_fields top_label description_below">
                <li id="field_1_1" class="gfield gfield_contains_required">
                    <label class="gfield_label" for="support_content">Your feedback<span
                            class="gfield_required">*</span></label>

                    <div class="ginput_container">
                        <textarea id="support_content" class="textarea medium"  tabindex="1" rows="10" name="content" cols="50"></textarea></div>
                </li>
                <li id="field_1_4" class="gfield">
                    <label class="gfield_label"  for="support_email">Your email</label>

                    <div class="ginput_container">
                        <input id="support_email" type="text" value="" class="medium" tabindex="2" name="email">
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="gform_footer top_label">
            <input type="submit" id="gform_submit_button_1" class="button gform_button js-submit"  value="Send feedback" tabindex="3">
            <input type="hidden" value="support feedback" name="content_type" id="support_content_type"/>
            <input type="hidden" value="feedback" name="support_category" id="support_support_category"/>



        </div>

</div>

<p>If you want to send feedback about a specific page, go back to the page and use the “Is something wrong” link at the bottom of the page.</p>
